- PageRank

- Louvain Clustering

New experiment on Warpcast: featured frames

- Our goal is showcase high-quality frames to everyone using Warpcast
- Everyone can discover frames, developers can get discovered
- It's manually curated for now

"Won't it just be all the big accounts that win?"

1. We adjust for number of active followers, so big accounts get normalized a bit

2. We had a similar algo running every day since August with daily $5 USDC rewards

3. Accounts like @afrochicks started with few followers at the start of daily rewards and now have sizable (active) audiences.
